SecureWatch SIEM — Loyiha Tahlili

  Nima qurilgan?

  Bu to'liq stack Enterprise SIEM (Security Information and Event Management) tizimi. Uch asosiy qismdan iborat:

  Agent (endpoint)  →  Backend (FastAPI)  →  Frontend (React)
       ↓                     ↓                     ↓
  Log yig'ish          Analiz & alert          Dashboard

  ---
  Qanday muammolarga yechim bo'ladi?

  ---
  1. Ko'rmaslik muammosi (Visibility gap)

  Muammo: IT xavfsizlik bo'limi qaysi serverda nima bo'layotganini bilmaydi.

  Yechim: Agent barcha serverlarga o'rnatiladi va quyidagilarni markazga yuboradi:
  - auditd_collector — Linux audit loglari
  - journald_collector — systemd loglari
  - log_collector — ixtiyoriy log fayllari
  - process_monitor — jarayonlar monitoring
  - network_monitor — tarmoq ulanishlari
  - docker_collector — Docker konteynerlar

  ---
  2. Hujumni o'z vaqtida aniqlamaslik

  Muammo: Brute-force, lateral movement kabi hujumlar kech seziladi.

  Yechim: rule_engine.py — 4 qatlamli aniqlash tizimi:
  - Regex rules — pattern-ga mos loglar
  - Frequency rules — vaqt oynasida N marta takrorlansa (masalan: 60 sek ichida 5 ta SSH failure)
  - Brute force detector — SSH ga built-in
  - Composite patterns — murakkab hujum zanjirlari:
    - SSH login → sudo escalation = Lateral Movement (T1021.004)
    - sudo failures × N → success = Privilege Escalation (T1548.003)
    - login → cron job = Persistence (T1053.003)
    - /var/log fayli o'zgarsa = Defense Evasion (T1070.002)

  ---
  3. MITRE ATT&CK bilan bog'liq bo'lmaslik

  Muammo: Alert keladi, lekin bu qaysi hujum texnikasiga tegishli ekanligi noma'lum.

  Yechim: mitre.py — har bir event avtomatik MITRE ATT&CK ga maplanadi (50+ texnika). Masalan:
  - fim_modified → Defense Evasion, T1070
  - rootkit_detected → Defense Evasion, T1014
  - user_created → Persistence, T1136.001

  ---
  4. Zararli IP manzillarni bilmaslik

  Muammo: Tashqaridan ulanayotgan IP ning niyati noma'lum.

  Yechim: threat_intel.py — har bir IP uchun:
  - AbuseIPDB tekshiruvi (reputatsiya bali)
  - GeoIP (mamlakat, shahar, ISP)
  - Ma'lum scanner/botnet IP ro'yxati
  - TOR exit node aniqlash
  - Natija: alert darajasi avtomatik oshiriladi (level += 2)

  ---
  5. Fayl o'zgarishlarini sezmaslik (File Integrity)

  Muammo: Hacker tizim fayllarini o'zgartirib ketadi, sezilmaydi.

  Yechim: fim_realtime.py — Linux inotify orqali millisecond darajasida aniqlaydi:
  - Fayl o'zgarishi, o'chirilishi, yaratilishi
  - Ruxsatlar o'zgarishi (ATTRIB)
  - /etc/passwd, /etc/hosts, har qanday kritik fayl

  ---
  6. Rootkit va yashirin jarayonlar

  Muammo: Rootkit o'rnatilgan, lekin ko'rinmaydi.

  Yechim: rootcheck.py:
  - Yashirin jarayonlar — /proc vs ps solishtiradi
  - Shubhali kernel modullar — hide, rootkit, hook kabi nomlar
  - LD_PRELOAD hijack — /etc/ld.so.preload tekshiradi
  - Ma'lum rootkit fayllari ro'yxati
  - Kutilmagan SUID fayllar
  - Shubhali cron jobs (wget, curl, /tmp, netcat)

  ---
  7. Zaifliklar (Vulnerabilities)

  Muammo: Serverda qanday zaif paketlar borligini bilmaslik.

  Yechim: vuln_checker.py + nvd_checker.py:
  - OSV.dev API — PyPI, npm, Go, Maven, RubyGems, NuGet
  - NVD/USN — tizim paketlari (apt/rpm)
  - CVSS bali, fixed version, CVE ID ko'rsatiladi

  ---
  8. Compliance tekshiruvi (SCA)

  Muammo: Server "CIS Benchmark" yoki boshqa xavfsizlik standartlariga mos emas.

  Yechim: sca_collector.py — xavfsizlik konfiguratsiya tekshiruvi, score_% hisobi.

  ---
  9. Hujumga avtomatik javob bermaslik

  Muammo: Alert keladi, lekin kimdir qaror qilguncha vaqt o'tadi.

  Yechim: active_response.py — alert kelganda avtomatik:
  - IP ni bloklash (agent tomonida)
  - Email yuborish
  - Slack xabar yuborish
  - Cooldown tizimi (bir IP ni qayta-qayta bloklashdan himoya)

  ---
  10. Auditlanish yo'qligi

  Muammo: Kim qachon tizimda nima qilganini bilmaslik (compliance talablari).

  Yechim: audit_log.py + audit_service.py — barcha admin amallar loglanadi. CSV/JSON eksport ham bor.

